${BOLD}Session management:${RESET}
  amux register <name> [flags]   Register a session with Claude Code flags
  amux start <name>              Start a registered session in tmux
  amux exec <name> [flags]       Register + start in one step
  amux stop <name>               Stop a running session
  amux rm <name>                 Remove a session (stops if running)
  amux start-all                 Start all registered sessions
  amux stop-all                  Stop all running sessions

${BOLD}Interaction:${RESET}
  amux attach <name>             Attach to a running session (detach: Ctrl-b d)
  amux peek <name> [lines]       View last N lines without attaching (default: 30)
  amux send <name> <text>        Send text + Enter to a session
  amux send <name> --keys 'C-c'  Send raw key sequence (e.g., Ctrl-C)
  amux dispatch <name> [flags] <prompt>  Register + start + send prompt in one shot

${BOLD}Info:${RESET}
  amux ls                        List all sessions with status and previews
  amux info <name>               Show session config details
  amux defaults [show|edit|reset] Manage global default flags

${BOLD}Dashboard:${RESET}
  amux                           Interactive dashboard (optimized for phone)

${BOLD}Web Dashboard:${RESET}
  amux serve [port]              Start web dashboard (default: 8822)

${BOLD}Board:${RESET}
  amux board ls                  List all board issues
  amux board add <title>         Create a new issue
  amux board done <ID>           Mark issue as done
